37 §1730-B. Hospital facility price growth ceiling; maximum and minimum pricing
38 requirements for services
39 1. Definitions. For the purposes of this section, unless the context otherwise indicates,
40 the following terms have the following meanings.
41 A. "General hospital" has the same meaning as in section 7932, subsection 2-A.
